item.title: Beyond the Dark Woods
item.description: In a completely incomprehensible way, you ended up in the old witch’s house. Everything here smelled of damp and covered with cobwebs. Terrible place. We need to get out of here quickly. But first you need to examine the premises of the witch’s house very carefully in order to find items that can help find a way out.
